{"tid":1128153,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一隻新線上遊戲地帶既Game","createTime":"2019-04-27T15:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T18:47:08.000Z","uid":151858,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a4ff22693067a40b1a44b41f7787d5375905eeb8","tid":1128153,"uid":151858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"記得小學果陣成日玩新線上遊戲地帶<br />\n裹面有隻game係玩養啲圓形一粒粒既野好似係外星人定唔知係細菌<br />\n<br />\n跟住一粒一粒咁由BB養做大人<br />\n啲BB係綠色既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要餵野食比佢 跟住會成班走過去食<br />\n兩粒大人又可以生隻蛋變BB<br />\n啲蛋由佢就會孵化 收左佢就可以變做錢<br />\n佢會病跟住又要比藥佢食<br />\n老左就會變左灰色跟住就會死<br />\n<br />\n好似玩到咁上下有番咁多隻就會開始有啲紅色既好似蟹咁既敵人去攻擊佢地<br />\n要救其他就要犧牲是但一兩隻去打<br />\n好似可以強化一兩隻變左種做好打啲去打番啲蟹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後好似係成班搭UFO定飛船走就爆機？<br />\n呢個唔係好肯定<br />\nGoogle同係啲fresh game網到搵左好耐都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲玩過/有印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74d26afb98a65c4cec2caacf39ef282cfbc947e","tid":1128153,"uid":151858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c24fab9dc79805df8ab9679aec4e47ed56f7fa","tid":1128153,"uid":151858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999b547b5bd2bf2b8fae55bd0218e74607d26e28","tid":1128153,"uid":151858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"冇人玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38726fd8e8dc7a24c3c3532ceeae942f4ae6e91c","tid":1128153,"uid":226216,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"愛心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"7a63e46735ab83d5b4ee6ae5ae0487181933ff20","tid":1128153,"uid":151858,"